h.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170923%2F57244834&h=98378e1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170923/57244834</a></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n做咩姐你？</blockquote><br />\n尷尬..."},{"pid":"e2829ea57e751fed15deef7a3e0a6e8255cbe722","tid":410894,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:46:44.000Z","msg":"係香港啲閪佬賴曬皮啦"},{"pid":"ec4b06db204d28dc18ac4ccab31313c1c52936a0","tid":410894,"uid":21260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"外國教授真係好"},{"pid":"c0e2740d0139547b925fbd9703d2f7e918a4dec9","tid":410894,"uid":10509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:04:17.000Z","msg":"cheatsheet 寫得多唔一定考得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e09de07778dbc959021d808a681813a568fdaa","tid":410894,"uid":24634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cheatsheet 寫得多唔一定考得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會計考試應該都係抄多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627fcef5bdc0c7ca199be200f240038a937fe3cc","tid":410894,"uid":19557,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾得貓紙你<br />\n啫係有貓紙都冇用</blockquote><br />\n有d 係冇用 有d 係好有用 <br />\n有時可以幫你拎到好多分"},{"pid":"09d0ea86438b7d0b93da2d465b2a5c449b3d2236","tid":410894,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T12:07:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俾得貓紙你<br />\n啫係有貓紙都冇用</blockquote><br />\n有d 係冇用 有d 係好有用 <br />\n有時可以幫你拎到好多分</blockquote><br />\n不過睇佢托曬頭咁都係冇咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa